      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a reliable ride that's perfect for your daily commute! This car is in fair condition, showing some honest character and signs of use from its time on the road, but it remains a functional and dependable choice. It's a great opportunity to own a solid vehicle that\u2019s ready to keep on going!",
