    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable dings, some paint fading on the hood, and a few scuffs on the bumpers, while the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery and a cracked dashboard. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will soon require a suspension tune-up and new tires to ensure continued safety. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind putting in a little cosmetic work.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
